<h1>Welcome to Steve's Sock Shack!</h1>

<h2>In 2015, Steve G. wanted to create a store where people can express thier feelings and creativity...through socks.</h2>
<h2>The more stylish and sillier the sock, the better!</h2>
<hr>
<p><%= link_to "Add a New Sock", new_product_path %></p>
<hr>

<% if @products != nil %>
<h3>Here's a list of our socks!</h3>
<% @products.each do |product| %>
  <h3><%= link_to product.name, product_path(product) %>: $ <%= product.cost %></h3>
  <% end %>
  <% else %>
  <h2>No socks...yet</h2>
<% end %>
<hr>





<p>If your sock game is wack, then go to Steve's Sock Shack!</p>
